<section class="raffle-faq">
  <h2 class="raffle-faq__title">Questions</h2>

  <details class="raffle-faq__item">
    <summary class="raffle-faq__q">Who can enter the raffle?</summary>
    <p class="raffle-faq__a">
      Anyone 13 or older, anywhere in the world. Adults (19+) sign in with GitHub;
      teens (13-18) sign in through Stardance.
    </p>
  </details>

  <details class="raffle-faq__item">
    <summary class="raffle-faq__q">How does the raffle work?</summary>
    <p class="raffle-faq__a">
      Every week for 16 weeks we give away one AMD Radeon RX 9060 XT. You earn entries by
      signing up (1 base entry) and referring friends who join Stardance and link their
      Hack Club account (+20 entries each).
    </p>
  </details>

  <details class="raffle-faq__item">
    <summary class="raffle-faq__q">How do I earn entries?</summary>
    <p class="raffle-faq__a">
      You get <strong>1 base entry</strong> for the week you sign up. Then share your referral
      link. Each person who joins through it and links their Hack Club account earns you
      <strong class="raffle-pop">+20 entries</strong> for the current week.
    </p>
  </details>

  <details class="raffle-faq__item">
    <summary class="raffle-faq__q">What counts as a referral?</summary>
    <p class="raffle-faq__a">
      A referral counts when the person you referred links their Hack Club account on Stardance.
    </p>
  </details>

  <details class="raffle-faq__item">
    <summary class="raffle-faq__q">Do entries carry over between weeks?</summary>
    <p class="raffle-faq__a">
      No, each week starts fresh. Entries count toward the week they were earned in, so
      there's a new chance to win every single week.
    </p>
  </details>

  <details class="raffle-faq__item">
    <summary class="raffle-faq__q">Is it free to enter?</summary>
    <p class="raffle-faq__a">
      Yes. It's free, no purchase necessary. Just sign up on Stardance and share your link.
    </p>
  </details>

  <details class="raffle-faq__item">
    <summary class="raffle-faq__q">Will this cost me anything?</summary>
    <div class="raffle-faq__a">
      <p>If you're in the USA and win the GPU, absolutely not.</p>
      <p>
        If you're outside the USA and win the GPU, Hack Club will ship it to you from our
        HQ in Vermont, USA. We pay for the cost of the GPU and all shipping costs (which
        are quite expensive internationally!).
      </p>
      <p>
        Some countries charge money to receive packages from the USA called customs fees.
        This is a charge from your country, not from Hack Club, and sadly it's outside of
        our control. You can search online to try and estimate what this might be. Some
        countries don't charge anything and in some countries it can be crazy.
        <a href="https://www.newegg.com/gigabyte-gv-r9060xtgaming-oc-16gd-radeon-rx-9060-xt-16gb-graphics-card-triple-fans/p/N82E16814932806" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Here
        is a sample page to buy the GPU</a> so you can try and estimate for your country.
      </p>
    </div>
  </details>

</section>
